  'This Short was 100% auto-generated by the ViralOps AI pipeline.\n\nReal trending research via Perplexity AI.\nReal video via FFmpeg.\nReal upload via YouTube API.\n\n#shorts #viral #automation #ai',
  ['shorts', 'viral', 'automation', 'ai', 'aitools']
